module-DiscordContextMenu-MenuItem.html.name: MenuItem
module-DiscordContextMenu-MenuItem.html.description: This is the generic context menu item component. It is very extensible and will adapt it's type depending on the props. Note: The item ID should be unique to this item across the entire menu. If no id is provided, the system will use the label. Plugins should ensure there are no label conflicts if they do not wish to provide id. label conflicts (when not using unique ids) can cause multiple items to be hovered at once.
